(case suffix) Used to form the ablative case.
from (place)
A háztól jobbra van egy kert. ― To the right from the house there is a garden.
from, since (time)
reggel hattól nyolcig ― from six a.m. to eight a.m.
januártól ― since January

(case suffix) Used to form the ablative case.
from (place)
A kerttől jobbra van egy utca. ― To the right from the garden there is a street.
from, since (time)
reggel héttől nyolcig ― from seven a.m. to eight a.m.
decembertől ― since December
